flowchart TD
    A["🌍 1. Ordinary World\n(Status Quo — the customer's current painful reality)"]
    B["📣 2. Call to Adventure\n(A triggering event forces recognition of the problem)"]
    C["🚫 3. Refusal of the Call\n(Resistance to change: cost, disruption, uncertainty)"]
    D["🤝 4. Meeting the Mentor\n(The customer discovers your brand via content or referral)"]
    E["🚪 5. Crossing the Threshold\n(First commitment: demo request, trial, or pilot)"]
    F["⚔️ 6. Tests, Allies, Enemies\n(Internal politics, IT security concerns, champions)"]
    G["🏔️ 7. Approach to the Cave\n(The biggest implementation challenge looms)"]
    H["🔥 8. Ordeal\n(Overcoming the core obstacle: migration, change management)"]
    I["🏆 9. Reward\n(Initial success — the first win that validates the decision)"]
    J["🔄 10. The Road Back\n(Integration into daily operations and workflows)"]
    K["⚡ 11. Resurrection\n(Final challenge to full adoption and scale)"]
    L["✨ 12. Return with the Elixir\n(Transformation complete — the customer becomes an advocate)"]

    A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F --> G --> H --> I --> J --> K --> L

